OL,3,CFarmer 'disheartened' after nearly 80
OL,4,Cbags of marijuana dumped on land
OL,6,FA Gower farmer has shared his
OL,7,Ffrustration after waking up to find
OL,8,Fnearly 80 bin bags of marijuana dumped
OL,9,Fon his land.
OL,11,FRob Morgan discovered the large pile
OL,12,Fof rubbish in one of his Christmas
OL,13,Ftree fields, where the bags were
OL,14,Ffilled with marijuana plants, rubber
OL,15,Fgloves and aerosol cans.
OL,17,FRob took to social media to reveal the
OL,18,Fshocking site to his followers,
OL,19,Fdescribing the situation as
OL,20,F"disgusting".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
