OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779462670
OL,3,CFarmer 'disheartened' after nearly 80
OL,4,Cbags of marijuana dumped on land
OL,6,FIn a Facebook video, he said: "Sadly
OL,7,Fthey've driven into our farm, and just
OL,8,Fdumped the bags off. It's pretty
OL,9,Fdisgusting."
OL,11,F"I'm trying to make money as a
OL,12,Ffarmer...it takes 12 years to grow a
OL,13,FChristmas tree. It probably took them
OL,14,F3 months to grow all of this. Now it
OL,15,Fis another cost to us, getting rid of
OL,16,Fall the bags".
OL,18,FRob also told ITV News he felted
OL,19,F"disheartened" that his farm had been
OL,20,Ftargeted. He now has plans to pay for
OL,21,Fmore security around his land.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
