PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779462670
OL,3,CFarmer 'disheartened' after nearly 80
OL,4,Cbags of marijuana dumped on land
OL,6,FA spokesperson from South Wales Police
OL,7,Fsaid: "Officers received a report of
OL,8,F75-80 bags of waste illegally dumped
OL,9,Fin proximity to Sunnyside Farm, Chapel
OL,10,FRoad, Three Crosses, Swansea shortly
OL,11,Fbefore 2pm on Tuesday May 19.
OL,13,F"The waste contains what appears to be
OL,14,Fremnants from a cannabis factory.
OL,16,F"The local authority's environment
OL,17,Fdepartment has been contacted to
OL,18,Fattend and remove the waste.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
